com.here.android.mpa.search

Class Link

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.search.Link
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DiscoveryResult, ReportingLink, SupplierLink, UserLink, ViaLink

    public class Link
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Link indicating that the application must make another request to retrieve the desired resource.

    Note: a Link contains metadata about the linked resource.
